lead_paragraph: Brandon Dubinsky scored the only shootout goal in the third round, and Scott Hartnell had a goal and assist as the hot Columbus Blue Jackets beat the Atlantic Division-leading Florida Panthers 4-3 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Dubinsky Nets Lone SO Goal to Send Columbus Past Florida 4-3
